                <span class="card-title"> Media and the Movement</span>
                <p class="truncate"> Media and the Movement: Journalism, Civil Rights, and Black Power in the American South is an oral history project that aims to understand the media and activism ecosystem of the American South during the civil rights movement of the 1960s, 1970s, and 1980s.</p>
