                <p class="truncate"> In 2016, the confederate monument on the campus of the University of North Carolina, Chapel Hill (UNC), nicknamed “Silent Sam,” was beginning to attract attention on twitter with the hashtag #SilentSam. The social media data group at UNC are creating a series of visualizations that will continually update, allowing an interactive, real time experience of the conversation surrounding the controversy .</p>
